data.description: "Serious Sellers here, in the market reduce $50,000" See Agent Remarks for 1,413 Sq Ft adjustment, an entertaining dream home, updated new 36 x 13 custom pool w/8x8 spa- both have a heater/cooler. Custom landscaping / lighting, fence, circular drive. Updated modern 3 bedroom 2 bath, turn key ready with plenty of expansion space, steel roof, newly painted exterior, kitchen, electrical, irrigation system, new plumbing and much more. So many features to list of upgrades, open concept chef’s kitchen, with stainless appliances, built-in dining room cabinets, laundry room/half bath with large pantry storage, outdoor shower, storage shed, sunroom dining/family room. New outdoor pool, patio and entertaining space indoors and out for everyone. Exterior door into 1/2 bath/laundry its own a/c system.
